description: Lola comes into this Lola comes into this match 0-1. What did she learn from her previous match? What experience did she gain to help her against Donna (The Spider)? The Spider soon had Lola tied up in her long legs and arms. Lola was totally helpless against the spider, as she was fingered, taunted and put into many painful scissors holds. Escape was impossible, and Lola became The Spider's bitch.
title: Lola and Princess Donna Dolore
